Oops is one the important concept i java. which talk about object.
there are four type of oops concept:
1] Encapsulation
   Encapsulation is the oops concept which secure the object.achieve encapsulation by making class member private(variable) and final(method).
   Use getter and setter method to get and set value in another class.

2]Inheritance
  In inheritance one class use code of another class and avoid the code duplication.
  It is like parent-child relation.child acquire property from parent.
  types:
  a] Single-level
  b] Multi-level
  c] Multiple     (not support in java through classes but support through interface)
  d] Hierarchical

3] Polymorphism
    One object behave differently
     a] Method-overloading   (compile time)
     b]Method-overriding       (run time)

4] Abstraction
    Show functionality and hide the implementation.
    Achieve abstraction using abstract class and interface.





